  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 394e3525f288a3649be30b055ab1ef28, type: 3}
  m_Name: Nostalgic
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueNode
  npcName: Alty
  _npcRating: 0
  _isFinalNode: 0
  _lines:
  - Sometimes I think I've moved on...
  - Then I'll fall right back into place.
  - I suppose the years may be getting to me.
  - It takes a lot out of someone to break out of old habits.
  - But I wanna say I've done good...
  - I've shown kindness...
  - I've shown care...
  - And if the time come...
  - If I were to face being forgotten...
  - I wanna say that I gave all I had.
  _playerReplyOptions:
  - How noble...
  - You've certainly been very kind to me.
